main event: Multiple unidentified flying objects were observed in Corry, Pennsylvania, displaying unusual flight characteristics.
interesting points: The objects were reported to be larger than a star and moving slowly and quickly in straight lines without any sound., Observers noted that the objects were white and discoidal in shape., The sighting included a case where one object was seen hovering silently over a golf course., Some of the objects were described to have a luminous corona and performed erratic maneuvers., The investigation noted that the majority of UFO reports were misidentifications or hoaxes, but a small percentage remain unexplained.
